Emergency staff were on scene and a portion of the N2 remained closed to traffic as a result of the accident. CAPE TOWN A motorist has been killed and two others injured during a collision between four cars on the N2 Highway at the Stilbaai offramp.Emergency staff were on scene and the road remained closed to traffic as a result of the accident.Western Cape traffic Chief Kenny Africa said: Apparently a light motor vehicle and an LDV were involved in a head-on collision and another two vehicles also collided with the two. The road is still closed to traffic due to this bad accident. 